text: Gauri Sandip Gokhale (born 5 May 1984) is a Maharashtrian cricketer.Player's Profile She played for Mumbai and West zone. She has played 34 limited over and 9 Women's Twenty20 matches. == References == Category:1984 births Category:Mumbai women cricketers Category:West Zone women cricketers Category:Living people
